---
---

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer-grid">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <a href="/" class="logo">
          <span class="logo-icon">⬡</span>
          <span class="logo-text">Geode</span>
        </a>
        <p class="footer-desc">面向 Geometry Dash Geode 用户的中文安装、兼容性与故障排查指引。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-links">
        <h4>快速链接</h4>
        <a href="/mods">选择兼容模组</a>
        <a href="/recommend">新手选择清单</a>
        <a href="/install">安装与安全</a>
        <a href="/links">友情链接</a>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-links">
        <h4>社区</h4>
        <a href="https://discord.gg/geode" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discord</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/geode-sdk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/GeodeSDK" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Twitter</a>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-links">
        <h4>官方来源</h4>
        <a href="https://github.com/geode-sdk/geode" target="_blank" rel="noopener">开源代码</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/geode-sdk/geode/releases" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方 Releases</a>
        <a href="https://docs.geode-sdk.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方文档</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p class="copyright">非官方中文指南 · 以 Geode 官方资料为准</p>
      <div class="footer-badges">
        <span class="badge badge-success">
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z" />
          </svg>
          官方来源优先
        </span>
        <span class="badge badge-primary">
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14" />
            <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01" />
          </svg>
          开源项目
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0 var(--space-xl);
  }

  .footer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-bright);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .logo-icon {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .footer-desc {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .footer-links h4 {
    color: var(--color-text-bright);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .footer-links a {
    display: block;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    padding: var(--space-xs) 0;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .footer-links a:hover {
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .copyright {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .footer-badges {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
    }

    .footer-bottom {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-md);
      text-align: center;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
